              <a class="tag" href="http://docker.com/" target="_blank">Docker</a>
              <a class="tag" href="https://www.vagrantup.com/" target="_blank">Vagrant</a>
              <a class="tag" href="https://www.ansible.com/" target="_blank">Ansible</a>
